### ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
### FinFlow — Health Checks
### No authentication required for these endpoints
### Run these to confirm all services are UP before testing
### ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### [1] API Gateway Health
GET {{apiGatewayUrl}}/actuator/health

> {%
  client.test("API Gateway is UP", function() {
    client.assert(response.status === 200, "Expected 200 OK");
    client.assert(response.body.status === "UP",
      "Expected status UP");
  });
%}

###

